						<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[--Solivion's Camera
--!strict
--!native
--Things Are Constantly Checked Not To Be Nil, So Dont Worry Much About Those Warnings.
--Also Variable Wasted Left And Right, So It's Pretty Confusing.
